Far Sight
Discworld ritual help
Far Sight

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Far Sight -- Shows you an image of places far away, using an item as a focus.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
When far sight is performed on an item that has a location stored in 
it via remember place, it will give the Priest a vision of that location.
To perform this ritual successfully you need a Holy Symbol dedicated to your
God, and a prayer book containing the prayer "Sands through the hourglass".
.EP
